Donald F. Robillard Jr., CPA: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg








































  





















































































July 28, 2017 10:16 AM ET

Company Overview of ES Xplore, L.L.C.



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Donald F. Robillard Jr., CPAPresident and Director, ES Xplore, L.L.C.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 4 Board Members in 4 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships65--
Background

		Mr. Donald F. Robillard, Jr., also known as Don, CPA, serves as President and Director at ES Xplore, L.L.C. Mr. Robillard served as the Chief Financial Officer, Chief Risk Officer and Executive Vice President of Hunt Consolidated, Inc from July 2015 to January 31, 2017. Mr. Robillard served as Senior Vice President and Chief Financial Officer at Hunt since April 2007. Mr. Robillard is responsible for financings and continues to direct the treasury and insurance functions. ... He served as the Chief Financial Officer and Senior Vice President of Hunt Oil Company. He served as a Vice President of Financial Services at Hunt Consolidated Inc. He joined Hunt in 1983 as the Manager of International Accounting. Mr. Robillard served as a Vice President of Finance at Yemen Hunt Oil Company. He has over 35 years of experience in the oil and gas industry and over 20 years of senior management experience. Mr. Robillard has significant executive-level experience in the oil and gas industry, including experience with project financing for LNG facilities. His experiences in Yemen included his participation in the first oil from Yemen on to production, the development of 12 commercial oil fields and the construction of several major new gas facilities. He served with the international division of Cities Service Oil Company, where he held various supervisory and managerial accounting roles. Mr. Robillard serves as a Trustee of the Dallas Museum of Nature and Science. He has been a Director of Helmerich & Payne, Inc. since March 7, 2012 and Independent Director of Cheniere Energy, Inc., since September 11, 2014. He serves as a Director of Hunt Consolidated, Inc. He serves as Director at Cheniere Energy Partners LP Holdings, LLC. He serves as Secretary and a Member of the Board of Directors at Dallas Petroleum Club. He serves as a Vice Chair on the national board of Financial Executives International. He was recognized as one of the top corporate finance professionals in Dallas-Fort Worth as winner of D CEO magazine’s 2012 Financial Executives Awards, where he was honored as the Outstanding CFO, in the Private Company category. He is also a recipient of the 2012 Financial Executives International Distinguished Service Award. He is a Member of the American Institute of Certified Public Accountants, the Texas Society of Certified Public Accountants and the National Association of Corporate Directors. He is a Certified Public Accountant (CPA). Mr. Robillard earned a B.B.A. from the University of Texas in Austin.Read Full Background




