Donald F. Robillard Jr., CPA

Age : 65Public asset : 1,310,296 USDLinked companies :  Cheniere Energy, Inc. -  Helmerich & Payne, Inc. 





Summary 



Mr. Donald F. Robillard is a Member at Texas Society of Certified Public Accountants, a Member at The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants, a Member at The National Association of Corporate Directors, Inc. and Secretary at Dallas Petroleum Club.He is on the Board of Directors at Cheniere Energy, Inc., Helmerich & Payne, Inc., Hunt Oil Co., Inc. and Museum of Nature & Science. Mr. Robillard was previously employed as Senior VP, Chief Financial & Risk Officer by Hunt Consolidated, Inc., a Principal by Cities Service Oil & Gas Co., National Vice Chairman by Financial Executives International, and Vice President-Finance by Yemen Hunt Oil Co.He received his undergraduate degree from The University of Texas.



